<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">I don’t wanna be a hero, just wanna stay in the line</a></em></strong><br />
<strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">I’ll never be a Rob De Niro, for me Joe Pesci is fine</a></em></strong><br />
<strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">And so I follow my own rules and I use them as my tools</a></em></strong><br />
<strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">To stay alive</a></em></strong><br />
<strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">I don’t wanna be special, no, no</a></em></strong><br />
<strong><em><a href="https://youtu.be/l6Hp_ni5hus">I just wanna survive</a></em></strong></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><strong>—<em>More Than Survive (Be More Chill)</em></strong></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Yes I named this tale after a Be More Chill song don’t @ me we all knew this would happen</span></p>
<p>Wow, it feels good to post this. I’ve had this tale in the works for a good couple of months now, like almost a year or something? The thought came to me after reading <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5271378); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5271378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="Mew-ltiverse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5271378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5271378); return false;">Mew-ltiverse</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>'s collab con article <a href="/erics-journal">Eric's Journal</a> and realizing applying the same principle to an older Eric article might yield some interesting results.</p>
<p>Thanks to my critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6001754); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6001754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="barredowl" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6001754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6001754); return false;">barredowl</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242824&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="The Pighead" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242824)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;">The Pighead</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;">AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span>, and especially to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5271378); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5271378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594152387" alt="Mew-ltiverse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5271378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5271378); return false;">Mew-ltiverse</a></span> who encouraged me to make this and for looking at, brainstorming, and critting this article over the nine months or so I've been working on it.</p>
<p>If you liked this, <a href="/oboebandgeek99">consider checking out some of my other articles.</a></p>

